{"tid":972353,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再蝦我軒軒！！！(張敬軒)","createTime":"2019-01-07T10:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T11:44:32.000Z","uid":118455,"like":77,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9916cb3f3698257e07daeceb4dc403b5c653b8","tid":972353,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"呢排見好多PO都係到話我軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話佢奶共, 入左英皇個人假左呀, 係廣州鄕下仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 作為資深FAN表示心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望軒仔唔好理人點睇佢啦, 都有我地資深FANS 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;張敬軒出生於<strong>廣州</strong>，畢業於東山培正小學，廣州市第七中學和廣州市五羊金融經濟職業學校。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但首先人地真係廣州人wo, 小學, 中學, 高中都係廣州讀, 身份認同自己係廣州人中國人有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根據 &quot;軒與他們的地產&quot; 佢最後都話自己第時百年歸老都會選擇留番廣州。人地認為自己既根係廣州, 但同時唔想中國政治入左香港, e.g.通過國民教育, 所以想保護香港學生, 但唔代表人地就係港獨嫁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。係連登仔一箱情願, 一開始人地為香港發聲支持雨傘就假設左人地支持港獨。<br />\n當有其他明星, e.g. hocc 既立場咁左派, 再睇下佢以前同而家發展既分別, 又少左好多大品牌肯用, 某d連登仔 除左一開始上下連登講2句之外, 實則有咩支持過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人自己都唔橕自己人, 都團結唔到, 重好意思話人地&quot;廣州鄕下仔&quot;唔幫香港。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「他們用各種渠道指責我」官二代張敬軒反國教被封嘴:</strong><br />\n【娛圈反國教】一場反洗腦抗爭，令挺身撐學民思潮的藝人面臨白色威脅，繼演員杜汶澤被收聲、著名填詞人黃偉文收恐嚇短訊後，第三位受害者就是連日為孩子們發聲的歌手張敬軒，身為內地官二代、父親是前黨委書記的軒仔，前晚在網上撰文自爆：「他們用各種渠道指責我！」他因愛家人惟有妥協，但絕不後悔：「人只要活着，就要活得明白。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20120909/18011201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120909%2F18011201&d=6F2wiYdL7XsyXFQWHa%2BeTSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=dda1ce3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120909%2F18011201&h=516b963f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20120909/18011201</a><br />\n一向以黎, 香港人都係功利主義, 90年代就算到而家有幾多人因為經濟政治等問題移民, 話就話&quot;香港精神&quot; 其實咪係個人利益為先, 香港有咩事?不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地軒仔都係為自己屋企人有咩問題, 某d連登仔係都要人表哂態撐港獨先得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時真係有咩事, 咪一開始講2下, 之後都冷不關心, 最梗要睇下食咩好西, 呃like。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;入左英皇好假呀, 變左&quot;<br />\n&quot;楊博士前楊博士後&quot;, 大佬果個係佢老細黎wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁人地又真係Dr.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你番大學唔通叫呀sir, miss 咩, 人地Dr, Professor 就跟番人地個稱謂叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再者, 又唔見你地同你老細講野西口西臉, 博炒咩。不過某D連登仔只係識得話人, 講一套做一套。<br />\n重有, 拍YOUTUBE 宣傳係公司安排, 你唔俾軒仔本身都ENJOR, 人有好多面, 一時認真一時FUN下有咩問題。係到要好似死硬派先得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留意得佢耐都知, 佢本身個人都中意講咸濕野, 搞下GAG咁, 只係係環球時無係呢方面發展。身邊好多80後D FD, 本身無咩留意佢但而家咁會主動傾佢。<br />\n不過想講你中唔中意都好, 佢呢個行為唔代表佢係&quot;變左&quot;, 人地本身就係咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英皇後:<br />\n1.好似係903頒獎, etc: 新人金 多謝軒仔, 又唔見咁多新人多謝其他前輩歌手, 因為一直軒軒都好提攜後輩, 想樂壇承傳到, 由以前到而家都無變過。<br />\n2. 同古天樂搞辦獨立音樂頒獎禮<br />\n3.月租20萬租歷史文物<br />\n4.仙后餐廳<br />\n<br />\n睇得出我軒無好支持本地文化, 音樂。而家有咩香港人咁有心呀?<br />\n某D ANTI成日用D人地自己都改變唔到既野, e.g. 出生黎攻擊人, 請問你地有咩好過人地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後附上我可愛軒相:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGyn4QK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGyn4QK.jpg&h=c8c91a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zgEnCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zgEnCq.jpg&h=2cb38446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTtO0o5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTtO0o5.jpg&h=610e938e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8ZFRvM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8ZFRvM.jpg&h=57922f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nJLiaM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nJLiaM.jpg&h=bdc4359a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQ4ZnCr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQ4ZnCr.jpg&h=3fe45e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7bkRvN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7bkRvN.jpg&h=88ca7842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GmEnCs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GmEnCs.jpg&h=8bccdde6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WqbAFpa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWqbAFpa.png&h=a16e5835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i29ZnCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi29ZnCw.jpg&h=8d258668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大左重靚仔左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a149a00d917c2aacad53c9e49e65134c9456a6","tid":972353,"uid":177089,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"明末清初，張敬軒多次於四川進行屠殺，造成四川人口驟減的現象<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/971823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/971823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e58f18aecb43651b1ccbfbe1c698